Package: nfc-lab
Architecture: amd64
Multi-Arch: foreign
Depends:
	qt6-base,
	libusb-1.0-0,
	libairspy,
	librtlsdr,
Description: NFC signal sniffer and protocol decoder
	NFC signal sniffer and protocol decoder using SDR receiver for demodulation and decoding 
	NFC-A, NFC-B, NFC-F and NFC-V signals in real-time up to 424 Kbps. 
	Logic analyzer for contact smart cards with protocol ISO7816.
